description:
Comic Related Roles

O'Connel voiced Captain Marvel in the Superman/Shazam!: The Return of Black Adam animated short film. He had previously provided the same role as Captain Marvel in one episode of the Justice League: Unlimited animated TV show.

O'Connel also voiced Nightwing in The Batman (2004) animated TV show

O'Connel will also provide his voice as Clark Kent/Superman in the Justice League: Throne of Atlantis (2015) animated film.
name: Jerry O'Connell
